Pizza + Sandwich = ❤️
Try this amazing recipe, you will love it.🤤😍

Prep Time: 15 mins
Cooking Time: 5 mins
Serves: 2-3

Ingredients -
1. 2 tbs Schezwan Chutney/Momos Chutney
2. 2 tbs Mayonnaise
3. Chopped Onion & Capsicum 🧅🫑
4. Sweet Corn (or any vegetable of your choice)
5. 1 ts Oregano 🌿
6. 1 ts Salt 🧂
7. 1 ts Chilly Flakes 🌶
8. Cheese Blend 🧀
9. Oil/Butter 🧈
10. Bread 🍞

Procedure -
1. Mix all the ingredients together and apply the mixture on the slice of the bread.
2. And place the another loaf on the top.
3. Now bake it or toast the bread. 👨‍🍳
4. Enjoy 😉

PANCAKES 🥞. That is all. 😉

Ingredients -
1. 1/2 Cup Maida (All Purpose Flour)
2. 1/2 ts Baking Powder
3. 1/4 ts Baking Soda
4. 1/4 ts Salt
5. 3 tbs Powder Sugar
6. Half Banana
7. 1 tbs Butter
8. 1/4 Cup Milk
9. Honey/Chocolate Syrup (For Topping)

Procedure -
1. Add all the things in the blender.
2. Blend the mixture.
3. Now put the pan on medium flame and apply little oil or butter.
4. Put the batter on the heated pan and let the batter cook from both the sides.
5. Enjoy your pancakes with honey or chocolate syrup.

Do Follow for Amazing food recipe videos @_lakshaysinghal_ ❤️
